K. Vijayan is an Indian film director predominantly having worked in Tamil cinema. He has mainly worked with Sivaji Ganesan and Kamal Haasan. He has also directed numerous films in Malayalam.
Samuthirakani of Nadodigal fame and K. S. Adhiyaman were once assistants to K. Vijayan. His son Sundar K. Vijayan has directed numerous television serials.

